## Fixed in Version 2024.10

Large number of MOS, plugin, licensing, printing, HTML5 integration and macro fixes.

---

## Limitations and Defects for Earlier Versions

Includes:

- Grace period delay
- Incorrect timing with predefined forms
- Diskcopy reporting
- Edit lock behaviour
- IME and localization issues
- Macro timing issues
- MAP story limit (20 devices)

---

## NRCS Tool

NRCS Tool supports login up to 20-character usernames only.

---

## Configuring Gmail SMTP Relay Server for Sendmail

Includes steps for:

- Generating Gmail application password
- Updating `/etc/mail/sendmail.mc`
- Modifying `/etc/mail/authinfo`
- Running `makemap`
- Restarting sendmail

---

